    {
      "blocks": [
        {
          "inline": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "The multi-dimensional FFT is computed as successive 1-D FFTs along each\naxis. The cost along axis "
            },
            {
              "kind": "emphasis",
              "text": "i"
            },
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": " is 5 * (N / d_i) * d_i * ceil(log2(d_i))\n= 5 * N * ceil(log2(d_i)). Summing over axes gives\n5 * N * sum(ceil(log2(d_i)))."
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Notes"
